Infrastructure as Code (IaC) automates infrastructure deployment using configuration files instead of manual setup.

Benefits:

* Consistency
* Speed
* Version control
* Automation

Examples in Azure:

* ARM Templates
* Bicep
* Terraform integration

For example, DevOps teams deploy identical cloud environments repeatedly.

A real-life use case is CI/CD automation.

Another example is disaster recovery provisioning.

IaC modernizes infrastructure operations.
